    public class FelixLauncher
extends AbstractFrameworkLauncher<BlueprintServiceListener>
    FrameworkLauncher implementation for the Apache Felix OSGi container. Uses BlueprintServiceListener instances, implying that the DependencyInjection and event mechanism is the OSGi [Aries] Blueprint framework.
